.TH "TEMPORAL.PLAINDATE.TOPLAINYEARMONTH" "3JS" "December 8, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Temporal.PlainDate.toPlainYearMonth \-
Temporal.PlainDate.prototype.toPlainYearMonth()
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]toPlainYearMonth()\f[B]\f[R] method of
\f[CR]Temporal.PlainDate\f[R] instances returns a new
\f[CR]Temporal.PlainYearMonth\f[R] object representing the
\f[CR]year\f[R] and \f[CR]month\f[R] of this date in the same calendar
system.
.SH SYNTAX
.IP
.EX
toPlainYearMonth()
.EE
.SS Parameters
None.
.SS Return value
A new \f[CR]Temporal.PlainYearMonth\f[R] object representing the
\f[CR]year\f[R] and \f[CR]month\f[R] of this date in the same calendar
system.
.SH EXAMPLES
.SS Using toPlainYearMonth()
.IP
.EX
\f[B]const\f[R] date = Temporal.PlainDate.from(\(dq2021\-07\-01\(dq);
\f[B]const\f[R] yearMonth = date.toPlainYearMonth();
console.log(yearMonth.toString()); \f[I]// 2021\-07\f[R]
.EE
